data.description: This stunning Chetco River waterfront home is a true masterpiece. Custom built with the finest attention to detail, this timber frame home offers a unique dual living arrangement with private entrances for each living quarter. The finished lower level even presents the opportunity for a potential third living space. The main and upper levels boast exquisite granite kitchens, spacious living areas, inviting dining spaces, expansive decks, comfortable bedrooms, high beamed wood ceilings, and breathtaking views extending across from the Coast Guard station. The panoramic views encompass lively maritime activities, captivating wildlife, bridge views, and awe-inspiring ocean-white water vistas. Beach access is a few steps away, close nearby!This home not only exudes luxury but is also designed for longevity. The radiant heat flooring ensures comfort throughout, while its construction is a testament to durability. Helical piers, securely embedded up to 22 feet deep into the bedrock, underscore the home's solid foundation and lasting quality. The practicality of a spacious 2-car garage and ample parking further complements this property.Be sure to request a viewing of the immersive 3D tour for a comprehensive experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional waterfront property yours.
